### ─── TEACHER ATTENDANCE ────────────────────────────────

### 23. Mark Attendance
POST http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/attendance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

{
  "classId": 1,
  "subjectId": 3,
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "lectureNo": 1,
  "records": [
    { "studentId": 1, "isPresent": true }
  ]
}

### 24. View Attendance
GET http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/attendance/1/3
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### 25. Update Attendance
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/attendance/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

{
  "records": [
    { "studentId": 1, "isPresent": false }
  ]
}

### ─── TEACHER MARKS ─────────────────────────────────────

### 26. Add Marks
POST http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/marks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

{
  "classId": 1,
  "subjectId": 3,
  "type": "INSEM1",
  "total": 30,
  "records": [
    { "studentId": 1, "obtained": 25 }
  ]
}

### 27. View Marks
GET http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/marks/1/3
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### 28. Update Marks
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/teacher/marks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

{
  "classId": 1,
  "subjectId": 3,
  "type": "INSEM1",
  "records": [
    { "studentId": 1, "obtained": 28 }
  ]
}

